_market_item.name: My First
_market_item.long_description: This template illustrates the basic usage of Xano Databases and APIs. A profile table is included along with 1 API group and 6 endpoints for CRUD (Create, Read, Update, and Delete) operations for that table. This template was created to help you get started with Xano, as well as visualize the connection between a backend and frontend.
_market_item.short_description: A basic template showcasing Xano usage.
